door
was
shut
against
the
lawyer.
“The
doctor
was
confined
to
the
house,”
Poole
said,
“and
saw
no
one.”
On
the
15th,
he
tried
again,
and
was
again
refused;
and
having
now
been
used
for
the
last
two
months
to
see
his
friend
almost
